text: Charles Miossec (25 December 1938 – 12 April 2020) was a French politician. He served as a Deputy from 1978 to 2002. He was born in Lanhouarneau, Finistère. Miossec died on 12 April 2020 at the age of 81. ==References== Category:1938 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Politicians from Brittany Category:People from Finistère
title: Charles Miossec
